<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">والبَيْعُ:</span> المَبِيْعُ.<span class="c5"> والجَميعُ:</span> البُيُوْعُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وامْرَأةٌ بائعٌ:</span> نافِقَةٌ لِجَمالِها.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وباعَهُ من السُّلْطانِ:</span> سَعَى به اليه.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">والبَيِّعَانِ:</span> البايعُ والمُشْتَري.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">والبِيْعَةُ:</span> كَنِيْسَةُ النصارى.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>